{"title":"芥末坛","authors":["王复羊","池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"芥末坛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伪劣药品销售，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不发愁担忧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奎宁、庆大霉素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磺胺、硝酸甘油……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管质劣价高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有办法出手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招揽大户买主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全凭付给回扣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凡是愿意进货，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一律奉送厚酬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佣金至少两成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外加彩电、洋酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大做肮脏交易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"次货供不应求。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"药厂从中获利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"医院借此创收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大夫分得好处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"病人吃尽苦头。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此卖药  王复羊 画  池北偶 诗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}